title: Vegan "Drama" is not Activism, It's Defamation, Ryan. (Happy Healthy Vegan, HHV)
description: We Don't Need Another Durianrider, we don't need another Vegan Cheetah --we don't need another 1000 people pretending to be these "micro-celebrities".  Instead, we need 10,000 people who are prepared to get organized, and bring paperwork to parliament, to the school board and to city hall.
